data.title: SKOG, IMO 8912039, Flag Norway
data.meta_description:
The current position of SKOG is at coordinates 58.6563 N / 5.5117 E, reported 21 minutes ago by AIS. The vessel is en route to the port of Sandnes, sailing at a speed of 10.9 knots and expected to arrive there on Aug 16, 1 AM.
The vessel SKOG (IMO: 8912039, MMSI 258006930) was built in 1991 (33 years old) and is currently sailing under the flag of Norway.
